#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.28"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.28:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.28:0.2"
msgid "3. Sattāvāsavagga"
msgstr "3. Abodes of Sentient Beings"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.28:0.3"
msgid "28. Dutiyaverasutta"
msgstr "28. Dangers and Threats (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.28:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti, "
"catūhi ca sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, so ākaṅkhamāno attanāva attānaṃ "
"byākareyya:"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, when a noble disciple has quelled five dangers and threats, and "
"has the four factors of stream-entry, they may, if they wish, declare of "
"themselves:"

msgctxt "an9.28:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto; sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.28:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti?"
msgstr "What are the five dangers and threats they have quelled?"

msgctxt "an9.28:2.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ, bhikkhave, pāṇātipātī pāṇātipātapaccayā diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, pāṇātipātā paṭivirato … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Anyone who kills living creatures creates dangers and threats both in the "
"present life and in lives to come, and experiences mental pain and sadness. "
"Anyone who refrains from killing living creatures creates no dangers and "
"threats either in the present life or in lives to come, and doesn’t "
"experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an9.28:2.3"
msgid "evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ hoti."
msgstr ""
"So that danger and threat is quelled for anyone who refrains from killing "
"living creatures."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.28:3.1"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, adinnādāyī … pe …"
msgstr "Anyone who steals … commits sexual misconduct … lies …"

msgctxt "an9.28:3.2"
msgid ""
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānapaccayā "
"diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, cetasikampi dukkhaṃ domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭivirato neva diṭṭhadhammikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ "
"pasavati, na samparāyikampi bhayaṃ veraṃ pasavati, na cetasikampi dukkhaṃ "
"domanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedeti."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who uses alcoholic drinks that cause negligence creates dangers and "
"threats both in the present life and in lives to come, and experiences "
"mental pain and sadness. Anyone who refrains from using alcoholic drinks "
"that cause negligence creates no dangers and threats either in the present "
"life or in lives to come, and doesn’t experience mental pain and sadness."

msgctxt "an9.28:3.3"
msgid ""
"Surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā paṭiviratassa evaṃ taṃ bhayaṃ veraṃ vūpasantaṃ "
"hoti."
msgstr ""
"So that danger and threat is quelled for anyone who refrains from using "
"alcoholic drinks that cause negligence."

msgctxt "an9.28:3.4"
msgid "Imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni honti."
msgstr "These are the five dangers and threats they have quelled."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an9.28:4.1"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti?"
msgstr "What are the four factors of stream-entry that they have?"

msgctxt "an9.28:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti:"
msgstr "When a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "an9.28:4.3"
msgid "‘itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an9.28:4.4"
msgid "Dhamme … pe …"
msgstr "the teaching …"

msgctxt "an9.28:4.5"
msgid "saṅghe …"
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

msgctxt "an9.28:4.6"
msgid ""
"ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti akhaṇḍehi acchiddehi asabalehi "
"akammāsehi bhujissehi viññuppasatthehi aparāmaṭṭhehi samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"And a noble disciple’s ethical conduct is loved by the noble ones, unbroken, "
"impeccable, spotless, and unmarred, liberating, praised by sensible people, "
"not mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "an9.28:4.7"
msgid "Imehi catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti."
msgstr "These are the four factors of stream-entry that they have."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.408"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an9.28:5.1"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa imāni pañca bhayāni verāni vūpasantāni "
"honti, imehi ca catūhi sotāpattiyaṅgehi samannāgato hoti, so ākaṅkhamāno "
"attanāva attānaṃ byākareyya:"
msgstr ""
"When a noble disciple has quelled these five dangers and threats, and has "
"these four factors of stream-entry, they may, if they wish, declare of "
"themselves:"

msgctxt "an9.28:5.2"
msgid ""
"‘khīṇanirayomhi khīṇatiracchānayoni khīṇapettivisayo "
"khīṇāpāyaduggativinipāto; sotāpannohamasmi avinipātadhammo niyato "
"sambodhiparāyaṇo’”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve finished with rebirth in hell, the animal realm, and the ghost realm. "
"I’ve finished with all places of loss, bad places, the underworld. I am a "
"stream-enterer! I’m not liable to be reborn in the underworld, and am bound "
"for awakening.’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.28:5.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
